m_Devlin\", \"score\": 0.9993620717236239, \"rank\": 0.0003480864282379413, \"text\": \"Devlin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Devlin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"BNB-Buddy's goal\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mostly, Milne said, changes will be limited to room renovations and a\\\"nice, new sign.\\\"\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"score\": 0.9999882805191259, \"rank\": 1.1664272371652896e-05, \"text\": \"Milne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"changes\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"renovations\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"a\\\"nice\", \"from\": 1218, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \", new sign\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Changing the name of the hotel was due to several factors, but dropping the\\\"motor-inn\\\"part was intentional, Milne said.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1346, \"end\": 1351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"score\": 0.9999882805191259, \"rank\": 1.1664272371652896e-05, \"text\": \"Milne\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/A._A._Milne\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the hotel\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"several factors\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"the\\\"motor-inn\\\"part\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than the older motor-inn style, Milne said it will have a more\\\"b